article_id:1111,category_name:News,title_name:A New Summon Showcase, A Dash of Disaster (Part One), Is Now Live!,image_path:,message:<div>A new Summon Showcase, A Dash of Disaster (Part One), went live <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1582869600"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>Featured adventurers and dragons currently have boosted appearance rates.</div><div><br></div><div>Newly featured adventurers and dragons:</div><div><br></div><div>■Adventurers</div><div>5★ Valerio (water/blade)</div><div>4★ Pipple (water/wand)</div><div><br></div><div>■Dragons</div><div>5★ Nimis (water)</div><div><br></div><div>・For information about other featured adventurers and dragons, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Appearance Rates and check the Appearance Rates section.</div><div><br></div><div>Availability period for featured summons:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1582869600"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1583992740"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Get a closer look at some of the newly featured adventurers and dragons below.</div><div><br></div><div>Featured adventurer:</div><div>
